quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  2,158,‘INNE ES-SEFA WEL-MERWETE MIN SHA’A’IRI ELLAHI FEMEN HEXHXHEL-BEJTE ‘EW A’TEMERE FELA XHUNAHE ‘ALEJHI ‘EN JETTEWWEFE BIHIMA WE MEN TETEWWE’A HAJRÆN FE’INNALL-LLAHE SHAKIRUN ‘ALIMUN
  2,159,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEKTUMUNE MA ‘ENZELNA MINEL-BEJJINATI WEL-HUDA MIN BA’DI MA BEJJENNAHU LILNNASI FIL-KITABI ‘ULA’IKE JEL’ANUHUMU ELLAHU WE JEL’ANUHUMUL-LA’INUNE
  2,160,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE TABU WE ‘ESLEHU WE BEJJENU FE’ULA’IKE ‘ETUBU ‘ALEJHIM WE ‘ENAT-TEWWABU ER-REHIMU
  2,161,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE MATU WE HUM KUFFARUN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ALEJHIM LA’NETU ELLAHI WEL-MELA’IKETI WE EN-NASI ‘EXHMA’INE
  2,162,HALIDINE FIHA LA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUMUL-’ADHABU WE LA HUM JUNDHERUNE
  2,163,WE ‘ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE ER-REHMANU ER-REHIMU
  2,164,‘INNE FI HALKI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE EHTILAFIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WEL-FULKI ELLETI TEXHRI FIL-BEHRI BIMA JENFA’U EN-NASE WE MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU MINE ES-SEMA’I MIN MA’IN FE’EHJA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA WE BETHTHE FIHA MIN KULLI DABBETIN WE TESRIFI ER-RIJ
  2,165,WE MINE EN-NASI MEN JETTEHIDHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ENDADÆN JUHIBBUNEHUM KEHUBBI ELLAHI WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ESHEDDU HUBBÆN LILLAHI WE LEW JERAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘IDH JEREWNEL-’ADHABE ‘ENNEL-KUWETE LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE SHEDIDUL-’ADHABI
  2,166,‘IDH TEBERRE’EL-LEDHINE ETTUBI’U MINEL-LEDHINE ETTEBA’U WE RE’EWL-’ADHABE WE TEKATTE’AT BIHIMUL-’ESBABU
  2,167,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ETTEBA’U LEW ‘ENNE LENA KERRETEN FENETEBERRE’E MINHUM KEMA TEBERRE’U MINNA KEDHALIKE JURIHIMU ELLAHU ‘A’MALEHUM HESERATIN ‘ALEJHIM WE MA HUM BIHARIXHINE MINE EN-NARI
  2,168,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KULU MIMMA FIL-’ERDI HELALÆN TEJJIBÆN WE LA TETTEBI’U HUTUWATI ESH-SHEJTANI ‘INNEHU LEKUM ‘ADUWUN MUBIN
  2,169,‘INNEMA JE’MURUKUM BIS-SU’I WEL-FEHSHA’I WE ‘EN TEKULU ‘ALA ELLAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  2,170,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM ETTEBI’U MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU KALU BEL NETTEBI’U MA ‘ELFEJNA ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’ENA ‘EWELEW KANE ‘ABA’UUHUM LA JA’KILUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JEHTEDUNE
  2,171,WE METHELUL-LEDHINE KEFERU KEMETHELIL-LEDHI JEN’IKU BIMA LA JESMA’U ‘ILLA DU’A’EN WE NIDA’EN SUMMUN BUKMUN ‘UMJUN FEHUM LA JA’KILUNE
  2,172,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KULU MIN TEJJIBATI MA REZEKNAKUM WE ESHKURU LILLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘IJAHU TA’BUDUNE
  2,173,‘INNEMA HERREME ‘ALEJKUMUL-MEJTETE WE ED-DEME WE LEHMEL-HINZIRI WE MA ‘UHILLE BIHI LIGAJRI ELLAHI FEMENI EDTURRE GAJRE BAGIN WE LA ‘ADIN FELA ‘ITHME ‘ALEJHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  2,174,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEKTUMUNE MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU MINEL-KITABI WE JESHTERUNE BIHI THEMENÆN KALILÆN ‘ULA’IKE MA JE’KULUNE FI BUTUNIHIM ‘ILLA EN-NARE WE LA JUKELLIMUHUMU ELLAHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE LA JUZEKKIHIM WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  2,175,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE ESHTEREW ED-DELALETE BIL-HUDA WEL-’ADHABE BIL-MEGFIRETI FEMA ‘ESBEREHUM ‘ALA EN-NARI
  2,176,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE NEZZELEL-KITABE BIL-HEKKI WE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE EHTELEFU FIL-KITABI LEFI SHIKAKIN BA’IDIN